{"word":"H4208 - מַזָּלָה - mazzâlâh - maz-zaw-law' - Planet","slug":"H4208","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַזָּלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mazzâlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maz-zaw-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Planet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D6;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - mazza&#x0302;la&#x0302;h</b> - <i>maz-zaw-law'</i><p/>Apparently from <a href=\"#/H5140\">H5140</a> in the sense of <i>raining</i>; a <i>constellation</i>, that is, Zodiacal sign (perhaps as affecting the weather): - planet. Compare <a href=\"#/H4216\">H4216</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4206\">H4206</a>"}]}